{icon:bullet,1.2}{c_important}Cache Rewards{/c} from {icon:Icon_Tooltip_Marker_Bounties_TurnIn, 1.5} {c_highlight}The Tree of Whispers{/c}
{icon:bullet,1.2}{icon:Icon_Tooltip_Marker_LocalEvent,1.5} completing {c_highlight}Local Events{/c}
{icon:bullet,1.2}{icon:Icon_Tooltip_NightmareDungeonEntrance,1.5} {c_highlight}Nightmare Dungeons{/c}
{icon:bullet,1.2}{icon:Icon_Tooltip_Marker_Salvage, 1.5} {c_important}Salvaging Sigils{/c} at the {icon:Icon_Tooltip_Marker_Essence, 1.5} {c_important}Occultist{/c}
